question: What is the name of the administrative center of Cēsu novads (Cēsis county) in Latvia?
asked_question_translated: Come si chiama il centro amministrativo di Cēsu novads (contea di Cēsis) in Lettonia?
answer: Il centro amministrativo di Cēsu novads in Lettonia si chiama Cēsis.
answer_translated_eng: The administrative centre of Cēsu novads in Latvia is called Cēsis.
